 Amina Elias","date":"November 27, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe most hesitant of people in killing are the people of faith.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 2666 Grade:\u00a0Hasan (fair) according to Al-Arna'ut Al-San'ani said, \"The meaning is that most people who avoid killing are the believers, because\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25705,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/29\/two-dua-seldom-rejected\/","url_meta":{"origin":10859,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Two supplications rarely turned away","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 29, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Sahl ibn Sa\u2019d reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTwo supplications are not rejected, or seldom rejected: the supplication at the call to prayer and at the time of the rain.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 2540 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0647\u0652\u0644\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1867,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/01\/21\/jihad-jus-in-bello\/","url_meta":{"origin":10859,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Jihad: March forward with the best behavior","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 21, 2012